Mary Jane Higby https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Jane_Higby 0 Mary Jane Higby (May 29, 1909 - February 1, 1986) was an American actress in the era of old-time radio and the early years of television. She is best known for her 18 years in the leading role on When a Girl Marries.
